VII. 🔐 Privacy + Ethics Layer (Non-Negotiable)

Rules
	•	Explicit consent for any human capture
	•	Auto-blur faces / remove identifiers
	•	No private spaces
	•	User ownership + deletion rights
	•	Sensitive zones blocked

⸻

System Design Choice

Process data ON DEVICE before upload when possible

Reduces risk massively.

