	•	royalties

⸻

3. 🕵️ Surveillance Drift

Fix:
	•	strict capture rules
	•	audit logs
	•	public transparency dashboards

⸻

4. 🎭 Reality Distortion

People stage fake scenarios.

Fix:
	•	randomness in quests
	•	cross-location comparison
	•	anomaly detection

⸻

5. 🧠 Incentive Addiction

People over-optimize behavior for rewards.

Fix:
	•	cap daily earnings curves
	•	encourage diversity of tasks
	•	cooldown systems

